title: Quick commission, Mid-laners
body: Here is a League themed painting I did.  Acrylic on illustration board.{{champion:268}} {{champion:238}}

replies.body: This is actually done in a style I don't get to see that much anymore. I really like it!
not my style but definitely good.

Wow!!! I really appreciate this so much! This is the first fan art that I have ever posted. Even though it was a commission, I expect to be posting more here. The reception I've gotten is ego boosting haha.
Wow, this is awesome. I love your style.
Zed kinda looks like Nocturne here. Great artwork!

No worries, all azir has to do is ult zed away and...

No wait that's not going to work on zed...

No wait that's not going to work on anyone 50% of the time...
It was a testament to the uncatchable nature of Zed and the buggy nature of Azir's ult.
I like your brush strokes. Good job!
